                                       <p>Whether you are in need of bi-folding doors for a kitchen extension, automatic doors for the office or are an architect seeking a reliable partner to work with, contact Dean today for a free, no-obligation quote.</p>
                                    </div>
                                 </section>
                              </div>
                           </div>
                        </div>
